{
  "voice_id": "7kXNOCqiaLdszL0OEXks",
  "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
  "voice_settings": {
    "stability": 0.65,
    "similarity_boost": 0.65,
    "style": 0.0,
    "speed": 1.1,
    "use_speaker_boost": true
  },
  "pronunciation_dictionary_locators": [
    {
      "pronunciation_dictionary_id": "AhK3J8mZDRoShxfoJLk6",
      "version_id": "pFvyQBbxEBKyF7C3IHpy"
    }
  ],
  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "It's 2026, and an AI agent can write the code for an entire video in under a minute.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4f33b2e438eaf8890d0bc08897d34713c05037fe1781c9cdb5cac208b00ac970",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 5.712108843537415,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "Two open-source frameworks are fighting over how it does it.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f57909a552f2476365c0405cc1cec0cda54f0f64bd433b89a04f476306cd8889",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 3.250793650793651,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 18
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "And yes \u2014 you don't have to know how to code to use either of them.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9d762060b8f579b195a9bdde05470bbe047e59dcb1e0b6287a7722f3768a4efa",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 4.6439909297052155,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 28
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Remotion. Versus HyperFrames. React versus HTML.",
      "checksum": "sha256:33544326ba2f4728679538e5cc2b225d51e752b3b14ae1be0da205c93b8a4ea6",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 3.5294331065759637,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 44
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "One of them is built explicitly for agents.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7203d4f8f6be737f125d6c6c0b8bd7e0592123d1b93e93ed6a53356c65ed112c",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 2.5541950113378684,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 50
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "Traditional video production hits a wall the moment you try to scale.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a604e08926c38600c14dc8a5dce5dfb34c0d201306b96dbe2aea170c47e8f658",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 3.8080725623582765,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 58
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "A human editor manually adjusting keyframes can't produce ten thousand personalized videos for a marketing campaign \u2014 not without an army.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1abaf2e437b0eecaf36ef783aa15b1f02e5de4aec8e83e4153c9b41ff18b4f5d",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 8.40562358276644,
      "word_count": 21,
      "words_offset": 70
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "That's the gap programmatic video fills.",
      "checksum": "sha256:bbeae3df05f5a8e67fdd2521bf089af689b67bd7fe3ad75d6febd972a4b8ae04",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 2.182675736961451,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 91
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "You write code. The code becomes the video.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b9d1c5e6c63872e66622f42c282b197b614e6cd9c44a554791ae3227a4dee239",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 2.786394557823129,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 97
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "It lives in Git, parameters come from a database, it deploys via CI/CD.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b0ee6b415a7c5804d175a72d95ccab0b2e21c2ee7b8a92c95ca2179d07052d00",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 4.96907029478458,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 105
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "By 2026, even the writing of that code has shifted to AI agents.",
      "checksum": "sha256:049c967ee48f6d3b4c66d27976c18e94339401a27cd9648816d9a5c2ff63412f",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 4.504671201814059,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 118
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "So if you're a beginner who has never touched JSX or webpack, you're not the audience that has to write this anymore \u2014 your AI coding agent is.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4d242fed1b5a4121b5b754658e45ef95fde21f088bf2b2520610c28159e27e0e",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 9.05578231292517,
      "word_count": 28,
      "words_offset": 131
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "Remotion and HyperFrames are the two dominant ways to do it.",
      "checksum": "sha256:cfc98fbd4fffcf354410de4288b3246a4322210117ec9e9f87131113ab576ab9",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 159
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "Remotion launched in 2021. Created by Jonny Burger in Zurich.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5c0550112b5595732117a4d21fecff10f74dc09d222679d4c19382e6925d52ac",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 4.31891156462585,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 170
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "It's the established standard with about forty-five thousand GitHub stars and five years of enterprise traction.",
      "checksum": "sha256:117a3756c5b723d77c9e3f6e35c9488f3e20c894793cff0c91c059eef620a318",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 6.362267573696145,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 180
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "You \u2014 or your agent \u2014 write the video as React components.",
      "checksum": "sha256:672126ec9508666dd96c67e1001a904a5eab6dba5242e02ff82049b54856857f",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 3.9938321995464854,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 196
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "JSX, TypeScript, hooks like useCurrentFrame \u2014 every developer tool you'd expect.",
      "checksum": "sha256:921e1dac5a0f87799cf88a20b8ac65fd0ab0115aa6ac391e65457e2d9b943694",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 4.96907029478458,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 208
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "HyperFrames went open-source on April seventeenth, 2026.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c5793c875165b511ff2eee54f9ec3a5a6c77ebeb0caa8b37003f13968e45744f",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 3.7616326530612243,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 219
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "Built by HeyGen \u2014 the AI video company that, according to industry reports, hit a hundred million in annual revenue last October.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7111c9e8e3bdb1e6069b01924be5be9ad818fe481c2d97595f48527069a15f3e",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 8.684263038548753,
      "word_count": 22,
      "words_offset": 226
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "Fourteen thousand stars in the first weeks.",
      "checksum": "sha256:beaa07f4a2529877fa9fca9d6e96b1904560a1d920a7704560b1d2c296e5a6c1",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 2.3219954648526078,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 248
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "text": "The video is plain HTML. No JSX, no build step, no React.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e6910441cb2e739cf09b8c3c87a326e8dd90f060ec8221e3ead19e065a8ec7de",
      "wav": "chunk-20.wav",
      "duration": 4.2260317460317465,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 255
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "text": "The split is philosophical. Remotion bets on React.",
      "checksum": "sha256:83da5afc8541daacb392ca5d4d914513b4a8abcaebc41d2e8c25d9d85e38fbfa",
      "wav": "chunk-21.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 267
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "text": "HyperFrames bets on the language LLMs already speak fluently.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e1dce120e35deaec4c59adb4aad89911f1d5c1437e209937334a245bece859cc",
      "wav": "chunk-22.wav",
      "duration": 3.7151927437641725,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 275
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "text": "Here's a moving square. In Remotion, the agent imports useCurrentFrame and interpolate, returns some JSX, and you're done.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9312462ea01328df3150ff416b490475ba7a008223da4063dac0a393bbaf4003",
      "wav": "chunk-23.wav",
      "duration": 7.198185941043084,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 284
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "text": "Clean. Type-safe. But it requires React knowledge under the hood, a build step through Webpack or Bun, and a node_modules folder with hundreds of packages.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2e923669a886b6e8da5b28db7b0e3ce0967b6f08d0ef0a3f57b42c8f1ce3e57a",
      "wav": "chunk-24.wav",
      "duration": 11.470657596371883,
      "word_count": 25,
      "words_offset": 302
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "text": "In HyperFrames, the same animation is a CSS keyframe inside a div with three data attributes. data-start, data-duration, data-track-index.",
      "checksum": "sha256:36d52e0d1549acbc1779c1f3e5f4f460edffd334ec2f1cbfbc42c90b0bf958f0",
      "wav": "chunk-25.wav",
      "duration": 9.148662131519274,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 327
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "text": "The browser plays it natively. Same square.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e6f354a473b5c326f45f6bfc6b1358b090fa221b9fab4e1340e4da3332ca170e",
      "wav": "chunk-26.wav",
      "duration": 2.5541950113378684,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 346
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "text": "One needs a build step. The other is just HTML.",
      "checksum": "sha256:315aa4289b0a7e39de786eb33bc14567fcc626a98ddb0e843ff9e1e09f5261cf",
      "wav": "chunk-27.wav",
      "duration": 3.01859410430839,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 353
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "text": "Both tools drive headless Chromium. Both are deterministic.",
      "checksum": "sha256:106856cbd16e061c8fdb20683961081682f965a4610f73b709803a03c6070b1f",
      "wav": "chunk-28.wav",
      "duration": 3.297233560090703,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 363
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "text": "The technical innovation in HyperFrames is something HeyGen calls the Frame Adapter.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4666d3bd265c3d60421d4f91f04e789025722da495099caa189f7ec76bf8d197",
      "wav": "chunk-29.wav",
      "duration": 4.551111111111111,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 371
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "text": "It hijacks the browser's internal clock with the beginFrame API, forces animation libraries like GSAP to abandon real-time execution, and steps through every frame manually.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3a5916fd5e67839b3303328ebf3aa8396a532fd2d8a99d2699c73f0281cfa92c",
      "wav": "chunk-30.wav",
      "duration": 10.681179138321996,
      "word_count": 25,
      "words_offset": 383
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "text": "There's a real test in HeyGen's own docs \u2014 a four-second GSAP animation rendered with Remotion compresses to about one second of motion plus three seconds of black, because GSAP runs on wall-clock and Remotion's per-frame evaluator misaligns with it.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d5c758c03bea1a028abdf9f5a805af1df2d34ce8683ea48bcee834f3a8cb3450",
      "wav": "chunk-31.wav",
      "duration": 16.253968253968253,
      "word_count": 40,
      "words_offset": 408
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "text": "HyperFrames handles it natively. Same HTML, every time, produces the same MP4.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e9ba173cac8a88b68eed91e56db679a41480fdd346d5489e0c8698e3501910a0",
      "wav": "chunk-32.wav",
      "duration": 5.433469387755102,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 448
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "text": "Let's bootstrap each one. For Remotion, the entry command is npx create-video at latest.",
      "checksum": "sha256:664a1f089cb4ac5a9f46b3c9fb6ad8cbbeda8a7421ef27b266ddfe5d3756d61e",
      "wav": "chunk-33.wav",
      "duration": 5.38702947845805,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 460
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "text": "It opens an interactive picker \u2014 nineteen templates ranging from Blank, Hello World, all the way to Three Fiber and Audiogram.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e28da973afa3c8701044d9c6e87bdb1051d1d7a5133b39ab6a0199942e5ea42b",
      "wav": "chunk-34.wav",
      "duration": 7.848344671201814,
      "word_count": 21,
      "words_offset": 474
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "text": "You arrow-key down, hit enter, then it asks for a project name.",
      "checksum": "sha256:78a3ae5e55c1ca01fc5882d0016b8247d2aa150ed864e3dbef0b763481923038",
      "wav": "chunk-35.wav",
      "duration": 3.6687528344671203,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 495
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "text": "Then comes npm install. That's where it gets heavy \u2014 hundreds of packages because of React, Webpack, the Remotion CLI, the studio, the bundler.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a09e92c98bdf6347b3ce2940d9cb383e193c315dfc431dd7098ee445e47fbfe0",
      "wav": "chunk-36.wav",
      "duration": 8.080544217687075,
      "word_count": 24,
      "words_offset": 507
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "text": "Once it's done, your agent edits the composition file, registers it in Root.tsx, sets the framerate in remotion.config.ts.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d03d8165e125e1d22172e17d5e9bbe6046d1286da737531d621ac009dcef3188",
      "wav": "chunk-37.wav",
      "duration": 8.544943310657596,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 531
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "text": "Then npm start launches Remotion Studio at localhost three thousand.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3654a72e69d9885987fb0f8f7f08d4b87688e0b8b3d4f14ba1f7645796f1a951",
      "wav": "chunk-38.wav",
      "duration": 4.272471655328798,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 549
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "text": "You get a full GUI with a scrubbable timeline.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ad94015b3b7c82722617e7024465e2bb34dbb2a6de6e6e771f1928a3fb1cd1d9",
      "wav": "chunk-39.wav",
      "duration": 2.7399546485260773,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 559
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "text": "It's polished. It's powerful. It's also a few minutes of setup.",
      "checksum": "sha256:551a6f0180ba071f0e5ffbf385e6d702f189fbc50f51631b4e48ff04263fb615",
      "wav": "chunk-40.wav",
      "duration": 3.9938321995464854,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 568
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "text": "For HyperFrames, the canonical command is npx hyperframes init my-video.",
      "checksum": "sha256:65fe9dd21e87a3b629f4737a79d84f8bab888c56fe4cf1871b43b00196bcb635",
      "wav": "chunk-41.wav",
      "duration": 4.4117913832199545,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 579
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "text": "It opens a small interactive picker with nine templates \u2014 Blank for empty scaffolding, plus named starters like Swiss Grid, Vignelli, and NYT Graph.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1474a0d0fd1421ef244a460733289af3c5d35ceca9049fe239bd9a8d46d97a14",
      "wav": "chunk-42.wav",
      "duration": 9.380861678004536,
      "word_count": 24,
      "words_offset": 589
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "text": "Pick one, hit enter. Six files appear. AGENTS.md, CLAUDE.md, hyperframes.json, an index.html under sixty lines, meta.json, and a package.json that's basically a thin wrapper around the hyperframes CLI.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9e792ada5659ec9df8464dfbbd32244fbe43b816467609f82d46104ee5b9ae68",
      "wav": "chunk-43.wav",
      "duration": 14.86077097505669,
      "word_count": 28,
      "words_offset": 613
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "text": "No npm install step. The post-init message tells you exactly what to do next.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9192e36c257377f05de26f3bdd0095fc76b908b3ba057d5e509fbf8957987ff8",
      "wav": "chunk-44.wav",
      "duration": 4.551111111111111,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 641
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "text": "Install the agent skill. Open the project with Claude Code or Cursor.",
      "checksum": "sha256:159354f6b2064e6c44f766fe7b01464a6b243292c123a235186dddf5bf94fdc0",
      "wav": "chunk-45.wav",
      "duration": 4.690430839002268,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 655
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "text": "Write a prompt in plain English. Render.",
      "checksum": "sha256:78ef8fd8ceb48899e369510aebda78a76043426485bf9273fbf11721ad979c2b",
      "wav": "chunk-46.wav",
      "duration": 2.3219954648526078,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 667
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "text": "The whole thing is built around the assumption that an AI agent will be doing the work \u2014 so even if you've never written a line of JavaScript, you describe what you want, the agent writes the code, you watch the result.",
      "checksum": "sha256:16a196b6198d545d4fe702d9090ebac8bebf079ae2db6fd4b4df519e8eb83061",
      "wav": "chunk-47.wav",
      "duration": 12.585215419501134,
      "word_count": 42,
      "words_offset": 674
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "text": "Now let's actually use them. You ask the agent to make the title bounce in.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1b3d02fd638ba65daa856e72a180ff75fd0777468e1edd06750fb0cff062a816",
      "wav": "chunk-48.wav",
      "duration": 3.9938321995464854,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 716
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "text": "In Remotion, it edits Composition.tsx, swaps interpolate for spring with damping config, saves.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b98117f7d195d1f1fe6447cedb28a5216d05c9bafc288538619188ca956bd6de",
      "wav": "chunk-49.wav",
      "duration": 6.2693877551020405,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 731
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "text": "Webpack rebuilds. The studio refreshes. You scrub the timeline.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6930c058e1b14bccb2c6fcbf6b3ab45e4906aca4caeb7ef29938012a7921bac8",
      "wav": "chunk-50.wav",
      "duration": 4.08671201814059,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 744
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "text": "Then you run npx remotion render to get the MP4.",
      "checksum": "sha256:cef153a72960fbc33a7e2eea7e0bdbd8339f885950c67bb84a75c17b2a3419a4",
      "wav": "chunk-51.wav",
      "duration": 3.01859410430839,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 753
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "text": "The render bundles the code, loads it in headless Chromium, walks the React reconciler at every frame, captures pixel buffers, encodes through FFmpeg.",
      "checksum": "sha256:142c837fc4f5a1ee7c2011cdf9b2c0f1796c910aa9d8272981de83427f4c5dc4",
      "wav": "chunk-52.wav",
      "duration": 8.870022675736962,
      "word_count": 23,
      "words_offset": 763
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "text": "Same task in HyperFrames. The agent edits a CSS keyframe in composition.html.",
      "checksum": "sha256:cd64cf27f2671f286063efb5034be981c866c55336b6bbb6c80ee4804bdeb384",
      "wav": "chunk-53.wav",
      "duration": 5.2477097505668935,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 786
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "text": "Save. Browser auto-reloads. No rebuild, no studio restart.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f6a01d80fb89e56389425a0c1da5835eb52f0338428ae9a9905f9cd9a6dd1b7d",
      "wav": "chunk-54.wav",
      "duration": 4.504671201814059,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 798
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "text": "To render, npx hyperframes render against the project directory.",
      "checksum": "sha256:94fb6717394448c8a394610a759c02ad3e08e3bdb3bc9c471cc428ffd13beefb",
      "wav": "chunk-55.wav",
      "duration": 3.7616326530612243,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 806
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "text": "Headless Chromium boots. The Frame Adapter pauses time.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b08d00308c18bf0de20b62baf828fd42dac4a8091e92908fbddfe6befd137fb7",
      "wav": "chunk-56.wav",
      "duration": 3.436553287981859,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 815
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "text": "Frames step deterministically. FFmpeg encodes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9d21d3792be00b2d3a54b55bb55aced472a7c36d46dcb2f09ec5391293431ac0",
      "wav": "chunk-57.wav",
      "duration": 3.0650340136054424,
      "word_count": 5,
      "words_offset": 823
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "text": "Same output. Different number of moving parts.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3437af72c0411c78866358ea4b7259d61e79948af83152d6cc258edc8a584226",
      "wav": "chunk-58.wav",
      "duration": 2.693514739229025,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 828
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "text": "And in both cases \u2014 you didn't write a single line of code yourself.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2033561cfe029273d94c1661f88b55992edb1fb7e5d692a18be016d84e8307fe",
      "wav": "chunk-59.wav",
      "duration": 4.597551020408163,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 835
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "text": "Here are real numbers from a clean machine.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a9b4ef4813565a05283ebc2417d37fd70b9c595f67585849403dbdec6ec6b4df",
      "wav": "chunk-60.wav",
      "duration": 2.414875283446712,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 849
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "text": "We cloned Remotion's official Hello World template, ran npm install \u2014 thirty-three seconds, two hundred seventy-eight megabytes, two hundred and five top-level packages \u2014 then rendered the default five-second clip in sixteen seconds.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5c34b67b2329dc1714c1035246744249b856e412126c28e5830f4fd7ffaaae9f",
      "wav": "chunk-61.wav",
      "duration": 14.953650793650795,
      "word_count": 33,
      "words_offset": 857
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "text": "We then ran HyperFrames init in a different folder, which finished instantly with no install at all, and rendered a five-second clip in seven seconds with a warm cache.",
      "checksum": "sha256:294054274cd16643d1d2274121deb44e3f09e000adbcedb7087edd667297653f",
      "wav": "chunk-62.wav",
      "duration": 10.170340136054422,
      "word_count": 29,
      "words_offset": 890
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "text": "Time to first video from a fresh project: Remotion fifty seconds, HyperFrames seven.",
      "checksum": "sha256:929fb46baa084705bd20b47e006a5929086a80bc3f66d0ca04dac7ed0bdbb14f",
      "wav": "chunk-63.wav",
      "duration": 5.015510204081632,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 919
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "text": "The render itself is comparable. The setup tax is where they diverge.",
      "checksum": "sha256:12f4794a997159c08560bca7d769248d8c8ac98f35069a69e43c08f724a99582",
      "wav": "chunk-64.wav",
      "duration": 4.179591836734694,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 932
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "text": "Head to head, here's where they actually differ.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8237226b1624bd5ad4149caff00a3b1d51ec9d3ee1120126a5406d88826a5ed8",
      "wav": "chunk-65.wav",
      "duration": 2.647074829931973,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 944
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "text": "Authoring: Remotion is React JSX. HyperFrames is plain HTML with data attributes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ef8cb308701a0afd964c434330cf61a31a3b9730d83ce8ea170c0fe733b64d75",
      "wav": "chunk-66.wav",
      "duration": 6.03718820861678,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 952
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "text": "Build step: Remotion requires Webpack, Bun, or Vite.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3fb2abcb238458ad8df05787b92f12c5c8b8e42d8650a9547f2505bc59ed5dbe",
      "wav": "chunk-67.wav",
      "duration": 3.250793650793651,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 964
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "text": "HyperFrames has no build step at all. Animation clock: Remotion evaluates frames mathematically.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8d7af500d66dab558fce93177c838d09ef737e1ac7e51858338999ef03e3b96d",
      "wav": "chunk-68.wav",
      "duration": 6.2693877551020405,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 972
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "text": "HyperFrames uses a seekable library clock.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1c405fecbf0058b142f876251e303dc1263159f9dce7dd09d70ebd84f11615e9",
      "wav": "chunk-69.wav",
      "duration": 2.647074829931973,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 985
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "text": "Distributed render: Remotion has remotion-lambda, the only production-proven distributed renderer in this space.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8edba50830bb36a97a48f0e4c55bf993f216ec91755aaa433fe638151bf65f33",
      "wav": "chunk-70.wav",
      "duration": 6.640907029478458,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 991
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "text": "HyperFrames runs single-machine in 2026.",
      "checksum": "sha256:48fc6d6af4211bc59ed74e001b4b0ba0ebbe87cab833519a5eda867d8d24eadf",
      "wav": "chunk-71.wav",
      "duration": 2.786394557823129,
      "word_count": 5,
      "words_offset": 1004
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "text": "Best fit: React engineers building deep video pipelines lean Remotion.",
      "checksum": "sha256:04e8f1bbe2ff562d130de72a16aa9e196607204eee174a3ab859f979d966a25d",
      "wav": "chunk-72.wav",
      "duration": 4.31891156462585,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 1009
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "text": "AI agents and prompt-driven workflows lean HyperFrames.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e0368b95974716ba2b5ac5bac896747d2018dd780d4bd93774e6c6d12d9b9ca4",
      "wav": "chunk-73.wav",
      "duration": 3.3436734693877552,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 1019
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "text": "The licensing split is the most concrete difference.",
      "checksum": "sha256:74ea092408168c8d5d0f467317bf3bf32700fdd08b5523f1ed5969a7ca87f34f",
      "wav": "chunk-74.wav",
      "duration": 2.7399546485260773,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 1026
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "text": "Remotion is free for individuals and companies up to three employees.",
      "checksum": "sha256:06ae02e41275c8fd683dee6c92c1ba69c3e868e2d97d1fd10e4743f0ca1b5282",
      "wav": "chunk-75.wav",
      "duration": 4.272471655328798,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 1034
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "text": "Above that, you're on a paid tier. The Creators plan is twenty-five dollars per seat per month.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6cf92fad8ea95eabd3f0099dc4e39c93c71e55fa243d49701f9038d333359ddd",
      "wav": "chunk-76.wav",
      "duration": 5.38702947845805,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 1045
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "text": "The Automators plan, designed for SaaS pipelines that render videos for end users, is one cent per render with a hundred dollar per month minimum.",
      "checksum": "sha256:21e05ac65cc92b0dd2ff8e64a8c23dd2b7e525ded4814e1faf71bf3ce2aceb87",
      "wav": "chunk-77.wav",
      "duration": 9.195102040816327,
      "word_count": 25,
      "words_offset": 1062
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "text": "Enterprise starts at five hundred. From version 5.0 forward, the Automators tier will require call-home telemetry through the remotion-licensing package.",
      "checksum": "sha256:88ab9ce6dfff889b51beff9c3ed78702393684a9b00fc604838056c921aff39b",
      "wav": "chunk-78.wav",
      "duration": 9.47374149659864,
      "word_count": 20,
      "words_offset": 1087
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "text": "HyperFrames is unconditionally Apache 2.0.",
      "checksum": "sha256:32d39a1dffd281ce39fa2010f6227771814e9bc17ccdfd5f999d6909653d1214",
      "wav": "chunk-79.wav",
      "duration": 2.972154195011338,
      "word_count": 5,
      "words_offset": 1107
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "text": "Zero per-render fees. Zero seat caps. Zero telemetry.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d0d7db21f3314286e2fcd25a33f7b013d544f4bc68bf96a76853fc10add80d3b",
      "wav": "chunk-80.wav",
      "duration": 3.4829931972789114,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 1112
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "text": "HeyGen monetizes the avatars and translation APIs, not the rendering engine.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ccd7588f02a1a026abd678347992821f871e73b05f241c285b7bfd15a11253bc",
      "wav": "chunk-81.wav",
      "duration": 5.340589569160998,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 1120
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "text": "They commoditize the engine and sell the AI on top.",
      "checksum": "sha256:31e8566e6e8aa6b814bab5ee82a9cd7709aadef1adb0076f496adcfa0598f5a5",
      "wav": "chunk-82.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 1131
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "text": "By cumulative metrics, Remotion is bigger.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f3e374ed010cca935d78f430c6b2d49df403fd50b9a8308677cd7e905185e69b",
      "wav": "chunk-83.wav",
      "duration": 2.36843537414966,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 1141
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "text": "About forty-five thousand stars over five years.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0e3dbf2d344976c4d9b8af11d3729dbb4baa871e8f33c03f262f3fd539128d2e",
      "wav": "chunk-84.wav",
      "duration": 2.8328344671201813,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 1147
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "text": "Three thousand forks. A thriving Discord.",
      "checksum": "sha256:97cfdf4b9a5c021ae6fdfe8645258766d3cd940819c4aeacf104dde64eedb291",
      "wav": "chunk-85.wav",
      "duration": 2.414875283446712,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 1154
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "text": "Trusted by enterprise customers including major tech companies.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9192066287e1e768e32d129b41900fb75e9e7978f87dd8d58fe8d5add62bbb52",
      "wav": "chunk-86.wav",
      "duration": 3.575873015873016,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 1160
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "text": "By new-adoption velocity, HyperFrames is moving faster.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3f315b3757bc75a39e761cbc84589a42a349e9331bd6a1d8a6d7c527f28975d9",
      "wav": "chunk-87.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 1168
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "text": "Fourteen thousand stars in weeks since launch.",
      "checksum": "sha256:014e3b2e57b5e469a5975ddc24904fd69beb0c897294e1590e5c6325ca504300",
      "wav": "chunk-88.wav",
      "duration": 2.507755102040816,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 1175
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "text": "Backed by HeyGen, which independent reports place at eighty-five thousand customers and a five hundred million dollar valuation.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4dfe68ba849aea33561c73c4b755793e4aa6de4895365df54e7d27a7d69c683b",
      "wav": "chunk-89.wav",
      "duration": 7.383945578231293,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 1182
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "text": "So who should use what. Use Remotion if you're a React or TypeScript engineer with existing component libraries \u2014 or if your agent is.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0dcd85cbeed93ce2c6c4dba527480bb0cc2767ca1c778f05135155c1f19fd901",
      "wav": "chunk-90.wav",
      "duration": 9.613061224489796,
      "word_count": 24,
      "words_offset": 1200
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "text": "If you need distributed rendering on Lambda for batch jobs.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7469f593ed37a0283599da2fc6f870f972e4ca420b035f5d8df7e6c067bd1d5c",
      "wav": "chunk-91.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 1224
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "text": "If you're building a video SaaS product where the type-safe component model is worth the setup tax.",
      "checksum": "sha256:722e45b25826aafe89f377dddf9fb13ed024a85a367dea80fc6aabf4e1fe251c",
      "wav": "chunk-92.wav",
      "duration": 5.340589569160998,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 1234
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "text": "Use HyperFrames if you're working primarily with AI coding agents \u2014 beginners welcome, no JavaScript required. If you want zero setup friction.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d7cc67f741eea5385effab59447721055f88712d971f17470d07ba8516b534d8",
      "wav": "chunk-93.wav",
      "duration": 8.870022675736962,
      "word_count": 22,
      "words_offset": 1251
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "text": "If you need the Apache 2.0 license for unconditional commercial use.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f33ba33ddfc6ba4c2f495c7613a0a214dd9e49ae8bf305757d9c2af7d0578869",
      "wav": "chunk-94.wav",
      "duration": 4.040272108843538,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 1273
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "text": "Or if you want to paste arbitrary HTML \u2014 landing page snippets, design system components \u2014 directly into a video.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ce3ec92274fa60bcfd41b3a9f270acc180bcbdf5470d72967d5ad1a190112510",
      "wav": "chunk-95.wav",
      "duration": 7.337505668934241,
      "word_count": 20,
      "words_offset": 1284
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "text": "Both are excellent. They're solving the same problem from opposite ends.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7dfb9c39c52f20facbb2d21ad524d7faca7017a52d0390ff039b4308785d08d1",
      "wav": "chunk-96.wav",
      "duration": 3.8080725623582765,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 1304
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "text": "The right answer depends on whether you're more comfortable in React or in HTML \u2014 and whether the human or the agent is doing the writing.",
      "checksum": "sha256:45968b2ddaaf9af6158de200c0e3f73dd7a6e0860d6037ccadfea4051c4b5f96",
      "wav": "chunk-97.wav",
      "duration": 8.17342403628118,
      "word_count": 26,
      "words_offset": 1315
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "text": "If you want more videos like this \u2014 agentic coding deep-dives, framework comparisons, real numbers from real machines \u2014 drop a comment below and subscribe.",
      "checksum": "sha256:241874804c37f7bf60a0580987553de07351386a323aedc482ccadc11fa731de",
      "wav": "chunk-98.wav",
      "duration": 10.216780045351474,
      "word_count": 25,
      "words_offset": 1341
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "text": "And tell me: React or HTML? Which side are you on?",
      "checksum": "sha256:bb770a040437ecb589d4014137849ba8da8db21ba112f661e04d6bf932d14217",
      "wav": "chunk-99.wav",
      "duration": 3.250793650793651,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 1366
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "text": "Links to both repositories and to every source for the numbers in this video are in the description.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9f9b002950d9d60637a05b93d48feecc8bca774d64f19a60256d8f650f31303a",
      "wav": "chunk-100.wav",
      "duration": 5.6656689342403626,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 1377
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "text": "Thanks for watching.",
      "checksum": "sha256:07f17ff4ae2970cfd5406d2784febcbf24785d33ccae41bbff2401f478248b75",
      "wav": "chunk-101.wav",
      "duration": 1.1609977324263039,
      "word_count": 3,
      "words_offset": 1395
    }
  ]
}